### Create reservation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "customerName": "林小满",
    "mobileNumber": "13800000001",
    "storeId": 1,
    "reservationDate": "2026-06-04",
    "reservationTime": "18:30",
    "partySize": 2,
    "preferences": ["quiet", "window"],
    "note": "靠窗"
  }
}

